{
  "stem": "521.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he says, at least a dozen people were eating rice on that day, because the rice was just boiling over, over, over, and people came with plates.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Now this was in Siberia.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not in the school, I couldn't say that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had professors in the school who were-- were rightists, like extreme rightists.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But in the school, they didn't practice it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They-- I was well-liked by most of the teachers-- we called them professors, even though it wasn't university-- because I was a quiet boy.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So if I wasn't very talented, at least I-- at least I behaved.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So this helped me a heck of a lot, because people like students who are not causing any trouble.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So-- so I got through high school.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I got-- I was supposed to take some kind of a job, between 1940 when I finished high school and between 1943 when I was taken to a forced labor camp.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I was in a shoe manufacturing business, and I have been there for about a year, year and a half.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Now, in Hungary, there were two anti-Jewish laws.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "One was in 1938, right after when Pius XII, who was called at that time Pacelli, who was celebrating Eucharistic Congress in Budapest.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "The minute he stepped out of the country, the first anti-Jewish law was enacted.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And at that time, my wife's father was exempted because he had silver and bronze decoration in the first World War.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "A year later, there was another anti-Jewish law, which one restricted the number of Jews who could be employed.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "There was only so many percentage who could be employed.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
